title: No Bullshit: Take Decisive Action, Unlock Your True Potential
description:
Are you happy with how your life is going? Are you spending most of your time consuming the genius of others, glued to Netflix andbecause you're unsure of where to go or what to do in life? 

If you died today, would you be happy with the impact you've had on the world? 

Most people graduating college feel totally unprepared for the 'real world'. I know, I was there. Undecided and apathetic for years, I finally managed to find my way out of the hole I was in, and now I want to share with you how I did it. 

If you're paralyzed by fear of making the wrong career choice
